00:00:27.180 --> 00:00:43.020
10.
Frog Smoothie

00:00:43.020 --> 00:01:46.380
Peruvians drink pulverized frogs blended with
herbs to combat asthma &amp; fertility issues.

00:01:46.380 --> 00:02:45.340
Though not scientifically proven, many residents
also drink it as a remedy for a low sex-drive.

00:02:45.340 --> 00:02:49.049
09.
Natural Orifice Surgery

00:02:49.049 --> 00:02:59.240
Patients have their abdominal organs removed
through their mouths or vaginas.

00:02:59.240 --> 00:03:12.220
The first operation saw a gall bladder extracted
through the mouth to avoid incisions.

00:03:12.220 --> 00:03:14.079
08.
Leeches

00:03:14.079 --> 00:03:20.878
Leeches remove pooled blood from blocked veins.
Also used to help heal skin grafts by removing

00:03:20.878 --> 00:03:21.878
blood collecting under the graft.

00:03:21.878 --> 00:03:22.878
07.
Maggot Therapy

00:03:22.878 --> 00:03:23.878
Maggots can be applied to wounds to remove
infected skin &amp; curb inflammation.

00:03:23.878 --> 00:03:24.878
They only eat dead tissue, leaving healthy
tissue untouched, speeding up the healing

00:03:24.878 --> 00:03:25.878
process.

00:03:25.878 --> 00:03:26.878
06.
Pregnant Horse Urine

00:03:26.878 --> 00:03:27.878
The urine of pregnant mares makes Premarin,
a hormone replacement treatment.

00:03:27.878 --> 00:03:28.878
In 2002, 9m women used Premarin until negative
side effects including heart attacks were

00:03:28.878 --> 00:03:29.878
reported.

00:03:29.878 --> 00:03:30.878
05.
Breast Milk

00:03:30.878 --> 00:03:31.878
Researchers have discovered a compound in
breast milk able to kill cancer cells.

00:03:31.878 --> 00:03:32.878
Studies led 1 patient to drink his daughter's
milk hoping to shrink tumors. Results were

00:03:32.878 --> 00:03:33.878
inconclusive.

00:03:33.878 --> 00:03:34.878
04.
Swallowing Live Fish

00:03:34.878 --> 00:03:35.878
Practiced in Southern India, asthmatics swallow
a 5 cm fish covered in herbal paste.

00:03:35.878 --> 00:03:36.878
Administered by 1 family who claim the fish
clears the throat, thousands visit them annually.

00:03:36.878 --> 00:03:37.878
03.
Intestinal Worm Therapy

00:03:37.878 --> 00:03:38.878
Parasitic worms are swallowed or crawl into
wounds to treat bowel disease &amp; ALS.

00:03:38.878 --> 00:03:39.878
Heightens the immune system that's been reduced
by modern-day cleanliness.

00:03:39.878 --> 00:03:40.878
02.
Tooth Transplanted into Eyes

00:03:40.878 --> 00:03:41.878
A tooth removed from the patient, placed in
the eye, can restore sight.

00:03:41.878 --> 00:03:42.878
A hole drilled in the tooth holds a prosthetic
lens. Implanted in the eye, it corrects corneal

00:03:42.878 --> 00:03:43.878
scars.

00:03:43.878 --> 00:03:44.878
01.
Fecal Microbiota Transplantation

00:03:44.878 --> 00:03:45.878
Donated feces are placed in patients suffering
from renal failure &amp; Crohn's disease.

00:03:45.878 --> 00:03:46.878
The feces replaces microbes missing from the
gut. Used since 4th century China where it

00:03:46.878 --> 00:03:46.883
was known as Yellow Soup.

